Package org.ejml.alg.dense.linsol.qr

Class Summary
AdjLinearSolverQr A solver for QR decomposition that can efficiently modify the previous decomposition when data is added or removed.
BaseLinearSolverQrp Base class for QR pivot based pseudo inverse classes.
LinearSolverQr A solver for a generic QR decomposition algorithm.
LinearSolverQrBlock64 Wrapper around BlockQrHouseHolderSolver that allows it to process DenseMatrix64F.
LinearSolverQrHouse QR decomposition can be used to solve for systems.
LinearSolverQrHouseCol QR decomposition can be used to solve for systems.
LinearSolverQrHouseTran QR decomposition can be used to solve for systems.
LinearSolverQrpHouseCol Performs a pseudo inverse solver using the QRColPivDecompositionHouseholderColumn decomposition directly.
SolvePseudoInverseQrp A pseudo inverse solver for a generic QR column pivot decomposition algorithm.
